<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="freopen" id="freopen">freopen</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">FILE</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">freopen</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>fname, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>mode, <span class="kw4">FILE</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>stream <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
freopen()函数用来将一个已经存在的文件流stream重新赋值（reassign）为另一文件和模式。这个函数调用后，给定的文件流stream将指向fname，存取权限由mode给出。freopen()成功时返回新的文件流，发生错误时则返回NULL。
</p>

<p>
参数mode和在<a href="fopen" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:fopen">fopen</a>中用法一样。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="fclose" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:fclose">fclose</a>, <a href="fopen" class="wikilink1" title="cn:c:io:fopen">fopen</a>
</p>

</div>
